title: Ebro In The Morning - Honoring Diddy + Free Brittney (Griner)
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/28/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio reminiscing over the BET Awards, talking about the recent Supreme Court decision to overturn Roe V Wade, and the incarceration of WNBA star Brittney Griner. 

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
